---
title: Creamy Pork & Israeli Couscous Bowl with Toasted Almonds & Garden Salad
description: Speed, ease and decadent deliciousness are the major themes of this dish. There's pearls of Israeli couscous and hearty pork
mince, stirred through a creamy Italian sauce for endless bites of 'yum'!

